Spring boot provides good platform for java developers  to develop and stand alone  and production grade spring applications that we can run

Advantages:
1) Easy to understand and develop spring applications.
2)Increases productivity
3)Decreases development time

Goals:
1)To avoid complex XML configuration  in spring
2) To develop a production ready spring applications in easier way.
3)To reduce the development time  and run the applications independently.
4)Offer an easier way of getting started  with web applications.
